c: 6
v: 112
t: "Uku niko twagiriye intumwa y’Imana iyariyo yose kuba ifise abansi bayo bamashetani mu bantu n’ibisigo, bamwe muribo baramenyeshejwe kuri bagenzi babo amajambo yukudandikanya kugira ngo babahende, rero iyo Umuremyi wawe abishaka ntibari kugira ibi vyose rero nubareke n’ububeshi bwabo"